  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个汽车维修领域的系统全景图。核心是一个叫MechBot 2.0x的智能诊断平台，它是整个生态的中心。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "mechbot",
        "plataforma de diagnóstico inteligente"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，MechBot 2.0x作为核心系统。那这个平台主要服务哪些用户角色？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "mechbot"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "有两类主要用户。第一类是车主，他们用手机App做自助诊断和预约维修；第二类是认证技师，他们在平台上接收故障预警和维修指导。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "owner",
        "dueño del vehículo",
        "mechanic",
        "técnico certificado"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我添加了两个Person节点：车主（Dueño del Vehículo）和认证技师（Técnico Certificado），并标注了他们的使用场景。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "owner",
        "mechanic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "数据来源方面，需要画一个外部系统——OBD-II车载诊断设备，它实时采集发动机、变速箱等遥测数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "obd",
        "dispositivo obd ii",
        "provee datos de telemetría"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "OBD-II设备是外部硬件系统对吧？我标记为System_Ext。它和MechBot之间是OBD主动上报数据？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "obd",
        "mechbot"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，OBD设备通过蜂窝网络或蓝牙把遥测数据推送给MechBot平台，关系是\"Envía datos via\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "obd",
        "mechbot",
        "envía datos via"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加OBD-II外部系统，并建立了指向MechBot的数据流向关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "obd",
        "mechbot",
        "rel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后还需要一个外部系统：合作车间的WMS和CRM系统，MechBot要跟他们做库存和预约的对接。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "workshop",
        "sistemas de taller",
        "wms/crm de talleres asociados",
        "integra con"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这个关系方向是MechBot主动去集成车间系统，还是双向的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "mechbot",
        "workshop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "MechBot作为上游平台，主动调用车间系统的API做数据同步，所以是MechBot指向workshop的\"Integra con\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "mechbot",
        "workshop",
        "integra con"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，车间系统已添加为外部系统，关系也画好了。现在回到用户侧，车主和技师分别怎么跟MechBot交互？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "owner",
        "mechanic",
        "mechbot"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "车主是\"Usa para\"，就是日常使用App做诊断和发起服务；技师是\"Consulta\"，更偏向专业查询和操作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "owner",
        "mechbot",
        "usa",
        "mechanic",
        "consulta"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "两条用户关系都加上了。我检查一下：车主→MechBot标注\"Usa para\"，技师→MechBot标注\"Consulta\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "owner",
        "mechanic",
        "mechbot",
        "usa",
        "consulta",
        "rel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，技师的描述我再说准确一点：他接收的是平台的主动推送，但也需要主动查询案例库，所以\"Consulta\"是对的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "mechanic",
        "recibe alertas y guías de reparación",
        "consulta"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下整体结构：中心是MechBot 2.0x智能诊断平台，上游数据源是OBD-II设备，下游对接车间系统，两侧服务车主和技师。对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "mechbot",
        "obd",
        "workshop",
        "owner",
        "mechanic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完全正确。图标题用\"System Landscape\"系统全景图。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c4context",
        "system landscape"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "标题已设置。所有元素和关系都就位了，我最终核对一遍：两个Person、一个核心System、两个System_Ext，共四条Rel关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "owner",
        "mechanic",
        "mechbot",
        "obd",
